channel.title: No-IP not working :l
channel.description: Well i made a No-IP account and everything and added my thing and entered it on Moparscape but it didn't work... yet it works fine with hamachi... what am i doing wrong? is there more to it than just making a No-Ip thingo? Please help!

item.title: No-IP not working :l
item.dc:creator: @0wn4g3_R4ng3 0wn4g3 R4ng3
item.description:
@0wn4g3_R4ng3 wrote:

If you don’t have a router, do this.

  1. Delete your No-IP address. Example: moparscape.no-ip.info
  2. Add it again
  3. Make a group called “MoparScape”
  4. Add your address to that group
  5. Done!

That’s what I do when my server won’t work.
